OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774786269
OL,3,CFirefighters called to multiple
OL,4,Cheathland blazes overnight
OL,6,FAround 60 firefighters have been
OL,7,Ftackling multiple heath fires in
OL,8,FDorset.
OL,10,FThe first alarm was raised at 6.53pm
OL,11,Fon Saturday, March 28th after an area
OL,12,Fof Sandford Heath near Wareham was
OL,13,Fspotted on fire.
OL,15,FAs crews raced to tackle the flames,
OL,16,Faffecting an area around 70m X 30m,
OL,17,Ffurther calls came in about two more
OL,18,Ffires at nearby Great Ovens Hill.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
