OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774786269
OL,3,CFirefighters called to multiple
OL,4,Cheathland blazes overnight
OL,6,FMultiple small 4x4 appliances and
OL,7,Fheavy off-road appliances, the Unimog
OL,8,Ffrom Wareham and water carriers were
OL,9,Fmobilised between the incidents.
OL,11,FThe largest fire was at Great Ovens
OL,12,FHill, covering an area of around 300m
OL,13,Fx 200m.
OL,15,FFirefighters tackled the blazes
OL,16,Fthroughout the evening and
OL,17,Fextinguished the fires by 01:00 on
OL,18,FSunday morning, the service said.
OL,20,FCrews have returned on Sunday morning
OL,21,Fto check for hot spots.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
